%sql
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS AIRLINE_DESTINATION_STAGING;
CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE AIRLINE_DESTINATION_STAGING (
DestOpenFlightsID INTEGER NOT NULL,
DestAirportName VARCHAR(100),
DestCity VARCHAR(50),
DestCountry VARCHAR(32),
DestIATA VARCHAR(16),
DestICAO VARCHAR(16),
DestLatitude REAL,
DestnLongitude REAL,
DestnAltitude REAL,
DestnTimezoneUTC REAL,
DestnDST VARCHAR(16),
DestTZTimeZone VARCHAR(30),
DestAirportType VARCHAR(16),
DestAirportDataSource VARCHAR(16))
USING csv OPTIONS(path '../../data/airline/DestinationAirports.csv');

%sql
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS AIRLINE_ORIGIN_STAGING;
CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE AIRLINE_ORIGIN_STAGING (
OriginOpenFlightsID	INTEGER NOT NULL,
OriginAirportName VARCHAR(100),
OriginCity VARCHAR(50),
OriginCountry VARCHAR(32),
OriginIATA VARCHAR(16),
OriginICAO VARCHAR(16),
OriginLatitude	REAL,
OriginLongitude	REAL,
OriginAltitude	REAL,
OriginTimezoneUTC REAL,
OriginDST VARCHAR(16),
OriginTZTimeZone VARCHAR(30),
OriginAirportType VARCHAR(16),
OriginAirportDataSource VARCHAR(16))
USING csv OPTIONS(path '../../data/airline/OriginAirports.csv');
